snippet.title: Farm Frenzy 2 | Gameplay Part 1 (Level 1 to 8)
snippet.description:
Grow grass for the farm animals, there is hens, pigs, cows and more. Stocking up your warehouse and shipping your goods off to market. When you earn enough money, you'll be able to upgrade your buildings to work faster and buy new equipment that can manufacture the goods consumers want. 

Farm Frenzy 2 playlist: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=la8VEvz48JU&list=PLWZSaUPVfKGb35BL1J_NUOIw6cUSjBCr5

Get Farm Frenzy 2 Here:
